- Separate user bot (`CorDiet_Bot`) and admin bot (`CorDietService_Bot`).
- Use inline keyboards for payments and CTAs.
- Prefer webhook mode over polling for production.
- Handle concurrency and retries gracefully.
- Log all key user actions to Supabase.